'''''Shuga''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''MTV Shuga''''', ni urukurikirane rw'ikinamico rwa televiziyo rwatangajwe bwa mbere mu Gushyingo 2009 kuri MTV Base mu rwego rwo kwitwa "MTV staying alive Ignite!" . Ibice byayo bibiri byambere byahawe inshingano na MTV Networks Africa ifatanije na MTV Staying Alive Foundation, PEPFAR, Ubufatanye bw’umuryango urwanya virusi itera SIDA (HFG) na Guverinoma ya [[Kenya]], mu rwego rwo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bugamije gukwirakwiza ubutumwa ku myitwarire yimibonano mpuzabitsina no kwihangana

Iyi filime yaje gukundwa cyane kandi yerekanwa mu bihugu 40 bitandukanye bya Afurika mbere yuko isohoka ku rwego mpuzamahanga kuri televiziyo zirenga 70.  Ikinamico yatekerezaga ko ari urukurikirane ruvuguruzanya cyane nabasekuruza bakuru ba Kenya kuko rwarimo amashusho amwe yarimo ibintu byerekeranye n'igitsina.  Yabonye igihembo cya Zahabu muri Gicurasi 2010 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry’itangazamakuru ryabereye i Hamburg mu [[Budage]] mu cyiciro cy’ubuzima rusange  kubera kwibanda ku rukundo, amarangamutima, n’imyitwarire y’imibonano mpuzabitsina mu rubyiruko rwo muri [[Kenya]]. 

== MTV Shuga (2020) ==
Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus, Shuga yagiye mu gitaramo gito cya nijoro cyiswe <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MTV_Shuga_Alone_Together" rel="mw:ExtLink" title="MTV Shuga Alone Together" class="mw-redirect cx-link" data-linkid="279">MTV Shuga Alone Together</a> kigaragaza ibibazo bya Coronavirus ku ya 20 Mata 2020. Iki gitaramo cyagombaga gutambuka amajoro 65 kandi abayishyigikiye barimo [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|Umuryango w’abibumbye]] .  Urukurikirane rushingiye muri [[Nijeriya]], [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] [[y'Epfo]], [[Kenya]] na [[Kote Divuwari|Côte D'Ivoire]] kandi inkuru isobanurwa n'ibiganiro kumurongo hagati yabantu nyamukuru. Inyandiko yanditswe na Tunde Aladese <ref name="writer" /> na Nkiru Njoku .  Nibo banditsi bakuru kuri iki gitaramo kandi banayoboye ibice. Gufata amashusho, kumurika no kwisiga byakozwe nabakinnyi ubwabo.
